    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but when i draw the tree, the branches for the PP seem to hang off the VP in a way that looks kinda messy. like, if i have multiple PPs, the whole tree structure gets really cluttered and complicated. is there a specific rule for how to keep the branching from getting too chaotic when a sentence is long?",
